#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:2
msgid "HTTPS"
msgstr "HTTPS"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:6
msgid ""
"HTTPS (HyperText Transfer Protocol over Secure Socket "
"Layer)可以理解为HTTP+SSL/TLS， 即 HTTP 下加入 SSL 层，HTTPS 的安全基础是 SSL。"
msgstr ""
"HTTPS (HyperText Transfer Protocol over Secure Socket Layer) can be "
"understood as HTTP plus SSL/TLS, that is, HTTP with an SSL layer added. "
"The security foundation of HTTPS is SSL."

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:9
msgid "交互"
msgstr "Interaction"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:12
msgid "证书验证阶段"
msgstr "Certificate Validation Phase"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:13
msgid "浏览器发起 HTTPS 请求"
msgstr "The browser initiates an HTTPS request"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:14
msgid "服务端返回 HTTPS 证书"
msgstr "The server returns the HTTPS certificate"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:15
msgid "其中证书包含："
msgstr "The certificate contains:"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:16
msgid "颁发机构信息"
msgstr "Certificate authority information"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:17
msgid "公钥"
msgstr "Public key"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:18
msgid "公司信息"
msgstr "Company information"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:19
msgid "域名"
msgstr "Domain name"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:20
msgid "有效期"
msgstr "Validity period"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:21
msgid "指纹"
msgstr "Fingerprint"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:22
msgid "客户端验证证书是否合法，如果不合法则提示告警"
msgstr "The client validates whether the certificate is legitimate and shows a warning if it is not"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:25
msgid "数据传输阶段"
msgstr "Data Transmission Phase"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:26
msgid "当证书验证合法后，在本地生成随机数"
msgstr "After the certificate is validated, a random number is generated locally"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:27
msgid "通过公钥加密随机数，并把加密后的随机数传输到服务端"
msgstr "The random number is encrypted with the public key and sent to the server"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:28
msgid "服务端通过私钥对随机数进行解密"
msgstr "The server decrypts the random number with the private key"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:29
msgid "服务端通过客户端传入的随机数构造对称加密算法，对返回结果内容进行加密后传输"
msgstr "The server uses the random number provided by the client to construct a symmetric encryption algorithm, encrypts the response content, and sends it back"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:32
msgid "CA"
msgstr "CA"

#: ../../source/network/http/https.rst:33
msgid ""
"CA (Certificate Authority) "
"是颁发数字证书的机构。是负责发放和管理数字证书的权威机构，并作为电子商务交易中受信任的第三方，承担公钥体系中公钥的合法性检验的责任。"
msgstr ""
"A CA (Certificate Authority) is an organization that issues digital "
"certificates. It is an authority responsible for issuing and managing "
"digital certificates. As a trusted third party in e-commerce transactions, "
"it is responsible for validating the legitimacy of public keys in the "
"public-key system."
